{"id":101,"ayahs":[{"number":141,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ يَتَرَبَّصُونَ بِكُمْ فَإِن كَانَ لَكُمْ فَتْحٌۭ مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ قَالُوٓا۟ أَلَمْ نَكُن مَّعَكُمْ وَإِن كَانَ لِلْكَٰفِرِينَ نَصِيبٌۭ قَالُوٓا۟ أَلَمْ نَسْتَحْوِذْ عَلَيْكُمْ وَنَمْنَعْكُم مِّنَ ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ ۚ فَٱللَّهُ يَحْكُمُ بَيْنَكُمْ يَوْمَ ٱلْقِيَٰمَةِ ۗ وَلَن يَجْعَلَ ٱللَّهُ لِلْكَٰفِرِينَ عَلَى ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ سَبِيلًا","translation":"who but wait to see what betides you: thus, if triumph comes to you from God, they say, \"Were we not on your side?\"- whereas if those who deny the truth are in luck, they say [to them], \"Have we not earned your affection by defending you against those be­lievers?'' But God will judge between you all on the Day of Resurrection; and never will God allow those who deny the truth to harm the believers.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/634.mp3","surahId":4,"words":[{"id":79198,"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/004_141_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79199,"position":2,"arabic":"يَتَرَبَّصُونَ","translation":"অপেক্ষা করে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_141_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79200,"position":3,"arabic":"بِكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের ব্যাপারে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_141_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79201,"position":4,"arabic":"فَإِن","translation":"যদি পরে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_141_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79202,"position":5,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/004_141_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79203,"position":6,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/004_141_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79204,"position":7,"arabic":"فَتْحٌۭ","translation":"বিজয়","audioUrl":"wbw/004_141_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79205,"position":8,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"পক্ষ হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_141_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":79206,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/004_141_009.mp3"